***************
Craft providers
***************

|doc-build-status-badge|_

Description
-----------
This project provides Python interfaces for instantiating and executing
builds for a variety of target environments.

Initial providers include:

- `LXD containers`_
- `Multipass VMs`_

Host support is targeted for:

- Linux
- Mac OS X
- Windows

License
-------
